&nbsp;the&nbsp;judges&nbsp;themselves&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;opening&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;22nd&nbsp;CUP&nbsp;Intramurals&nbsp;at&nbsp;Cuneta&nbsp;Astrodome,&nbsp;September&nbsp;13,&nbsp;2016.&nbsp;In&nbsp;the&nbsp;end,&nbsp;Alvarez&nbsp;surpasses&nbsp;the&nbsp;beauty&nbsp;of&nbsp;other&nbsp;candidates&nbsp;which&nbsp;made&nbsp;her&nbsp;the&nbsp;winner&nbsp;of&nbsp;Miss&nbsp;Intramurals,&nbsp;giving&nbsp;the&nbsp;College&nbsp;of&nbsp;Education&nbsp;a&nbsp;solid&nbsp;point&nbsp;that&nbsp;has&nbsp;been&nbsp;added&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;colleges&nbsp;collaborative&nbsp;points.&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;font-size:12.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;font-size:12.0000pt;">	</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;font-size:12.0000pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;The&nbsp;College&nbsp;of&nbsp;Education&nbsp;has&nbsp;been&nbsp;succesful&nbsp;for&nbsp;winning&nbsp;the&nbsp;title&nbsp;of&nbsp;Ms.&nbsp;Intramurals&nbsp;for&nbsp;three&nbsp;consecutive&nbsp;years.&nbsp;Ms&nbsp;Paula&nbsp;Mabute,&nbsp;BEED&nbsp;III-I&nbsp;in&nbsp;2014&nbsp;and&nbsp;Ms.&nbsp;Jonalyn&nbsp;Loterte,&nbsp;BSE&nbsp;IV-II&nbsp;(Math)&nbsp;in&nbsp;2015.&nbsp;With&nbsp;the&nbsp;success&nbsp;of&nbsp;every&nbsp;COEd&nbsp;muse,&nbsp;all&nbsp;female&nbsp;students&nbsp;from&nbsp;the&nbsp;College&nbsp;of&nbsp;Education&nbsp;are&nbsp;motivated&nbsp;to&nbsp;stay&nbsp;strong&nbsp;and&nbsp;beautiful&nbsp;to&nbsp;vie&nbsp;for&nbsp;their&nbsp;athletic&nbsp;beauty&nbsp;title.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;font-size:12.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><!--EndFragment-->');
INSERT INTO `news` (`id`, `title`, `author`, `slug`, `text`) VALUES
(13, 'EDITORIAL LINER: Teaching as a PASSION', 'Nicole B. Soer', 'editorial-liner-teaching-as-a-passion', '<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;font-size:12.0000pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"Teaching&nbsp;creates&nbsp;all&nbsp;professions."&nbsp;Teaching&nbsp;is&nbsp;not&nbsp;all&nbsp;about&nbsp;trying&nbsp;to&nbsp;make&nbsp;someone&nbsp;learn,&nbsp;but&nbsp;it&nbsp;is&nbsp;where&nbsp;in&nbsp;every&nbsp;lesson&nbsp;taught,&nbsp;where&nbsp;a&nbsp;legacy&nbsp;is&nbsp;left&nbsp;behind&nbsp;that&nbsp;is&nbsp;worth&nbsp;remembering.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;font-size:12.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;font-size:12.0000pt;">	</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;font-size:12.0000pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;As&nbsp;future&nbsp;educators,&nbsp;it&nbsp;is&nbsp;our&nbsp;main&nbsp;goal&nbsp;that&nbsp;we&nbsp;are&nbsp;trained&nbsp;to&nbsp;become&nbsp;responsible&nbsp;teachers&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;near&nbsp;future.&nbsp;It&nbsp;should&nbsp;never&nbsp;be&nbsp;forgotten&nbsp;that&nbsp;the&nbsp;art&nbsp;of&nbsp;teaching&nbsp;is&nbsp;found&nbsp;within&nbsp;the&nbsp;passionate&nbsp;heart&nbsp;of&nbsp;a&nbsp;teacher.&nbsp;They&nbsp;are&nbsp;very&nbsp;behind&nbsp;every&nbsp;miraculous&nbsp;hand&nbsp;of&nbsp;a&nbsp;doctor,&nbsp;every&nbsp;pillar&nbsp;built&nbsp;by&nbsp;an&nbsp;engineer,&nbsp;and&nbsp;behind&nbsp;every&nbsp;flight&nbsp;of&nbsp;a&nbsp;pilot.&nbsp;It&nbsp;is&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;heart&nbsp;of&nbsp;a&nbsp;teacher&nbsp;to&nbsp;always&nbsp;care&nbsp;for&nbsp;his&nbsp;students,&nbsp;to&nbsp;equally&nbsp;give&nbsp;each&nbsp;child&nbsp;a&nbsp;chance&nbsp;to&nbsp;unlock&nbsp;his&nbsp;potential.&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;font-size:12.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;font-size:12.0000pt;">	</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;font-size:12.0000pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;There&nbsp;are&nbsp;no&nbsp;perfect&nbsp;persons.&nbsp;We&nbsp;may&nbsp;occasionally&nbsp;commit&nbsp;mistakes&nbsp;and&nbsp;error&nbsp;but&nbsp;what&nbsp;matters&nbsp;most&nbsp;is&nbsp;that&nbsp;we&nbsp;would&nbsp;never&nbsp;give&nbsp;up&nbsp;on&nbsp;our&nbsp;challenges&nbsp;as&nbsp;teachers.&nbsp;We&nbsp;should&nbsp;take&nbsp;all&nbsp;the&nbsp;chances&nbsp;to&nbsp;be&nbsp;victorious&nbsp;in&nbsp;all&nbsp;our&nbsp;endeavors&nbsp;whatever&nbsp;risks&nbsp;it&nbsp;may&nbsp;take.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;font-size:12.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;font-size:12.0000pt;">	</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;font-size:12.0000pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Teaching&nbsp;requires&nbsp;passion.&nbsp;It&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;passion&nbsp;inside&nbsp;that&nbsp;gives&nbsp;out&nbsp;burning&nbsp;motivation&nbsp;to&nbsp;mold&nbsp;each&nbsp;student&nbsp;in&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;perfect&nbsp;future&nbsp;they&nbsp;wish&nbsp;to&nbsp;achieve.&nbsp;The&nbsp;key&nbsp;to&nbsp;a&nbsp;powerful&nbsp;teaching&nbsp;is&nbsp;to&nbsp;teach&nbsp;from&nbsp;the&nbsp;heart&nbsp;and&nbsp;to&nbsp;give&nbsp;our&nbsp;trust.&nbsp;To&nbsp;trust&nbsp;the&nbsp;surroundings&nbsp;and&nbsp;to&nbsp;trust&nbsp;oneself&nbsp;as&nbsp;well.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;font-size:12.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml><w:WordDocument><w:BrowserLevel>MicrosoftInternetExplorer4</w:BrowserLevel><w:DisplayHorizontalDrawin